      </list>
    </subsection>
    
    <subsection id="thematic-inspiration">
      <heading level="2">Thematic Inspiration</heading>
      
      <paragraph>
        This original screenplay was inspired by the philosophical themes
        of CodeBase by Christopher Johnson:
        the intersection of technology and humanity, the power of connection,
        and the realization that love is the greatest creation of all.
      </paragraph>
      
      <paragraph>
        This is an original work demonstrating how such themes can be
        adapted into romantic storytelling using the SPKML Screenplay Extension.
      </paragraph>
    </subsection>
  </section>

</spkml>

<!-- 
     RENDERING NOTES:
     
     This screenplay can be rendered as:
     
     1. INTERACTIVE HTML
        xsltproc screenplay-to-html.xslt CodeBase_Love_Story.spkml > output.html
        
     2. PDF SCRIPT
        Use wkhtmltopdf or Prince to convert HTML to professional screenplay PDF
        
     3. AUDIOBOOK MANIFEST
        Generate audio sync file with narration, dialogue, and music cues
        
     4. EPUB EBOOK
        Package as EPUB with embedded audio references
        
     This demonstrates the complete capability of SPKML to:
     - Author romantic storytelling with structure and semantics
     - Integrate multimedia (narration, sound design, music)
     - Transform to multiple output formats
     - Preserve content as open XML for decades
     
     The screenplay honors themes of the original work while being
     an entirely original creation suitable for professional adaptation.
-->
